description";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:269:"Meet <em>Canap√©</em>, a tasty new theme perfect for any food- or drink-related business.<img alt="" border="0" src="https://pixel.wp.com/b.gif?host=en.blog.wordpress.com&#038;blog=3584907&#038;post=33861&#038;subd=en.blog&#038;ref=&#038;feed=1" width="1" height="1" />";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:32:"http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/";a:1:{s:7:"creator";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:17:"Aleksandra Laczek";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:40:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/";a:1:{s:7:"encoded";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:2056:"<p>It‚Äôs the New Year, and we‚Äôre excited to kick it off with a new free theme!</p>\n<h3><a href="http://wordpress.com/themes/canape">Canap√©</a></h3>\n<p><a href="http://canapedemo.wordpress.com"><img class="alignnone wp-image-33862 size-full" src="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2015/12/canape_featured-image.jpg?w=720&#038;h=1526" alt="Canap√©" width="720" height="1526" /></a></p>\n<p><em>Canap√©</em> is a bold and refined theme, designed to help you create a beautiful online presence for your restaurant. Integrated with food menus, testimonials, and the Open Table widget, it‚Äôs the perfect choice for any food-related business.</p>\n<p><em>Canap√©</em> can be personalized to match your brand by adding a logo, tweaking the fonts, and choosing a color scheme from six¬†free palettes. The Front Page Template with a full-width featured image, featured menu sections, and three widget areas gives you ample opportunity to build a unique welcome page for your visitors.</p>\n<div data-shortcode="caption" id="attachment_33864" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img class="size-full wp-image-33864" src="https://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2015/12/canape_menu_short.jpg?w=720&#038;h=949" alt="Canap√©''s Menu Page Template" width="720" height="949" /><p class="wp-caption-text">Canap√©&#8217;s Menu Page Template</p></div>\n<p>Of course <em>Canap√©</em> is responsive, so your content will retain its elegant and sophisticated look on mobile, tablet, and desktop screens.</p>\n<p>Get to know <em>Canap√©</em>¬†on the <a href="https://wordpress.com/themes/canape">Theme Showcase</a>!</p><br />Filed under: <a href=''https://en.blog.wordpress.com/category/themes/''>Themes</a>  <a rel="nofollow" href="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/gocomments/en.blog.wordpress.com/33861/"><img alt="" border="0" src="http://feeds.wordpress.com/1.0/comments/en.blog.wordpress.com/33861/" /></a> <img alt="" border="0" src="https://pixel.wp.com/b.gif?host=en.blog.wordpress.com&#038;blog=3584907&#038;post=33861&#038;subd=en.blog&#038;ref=&#038;feed=1" width="1" height="1" />";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:36:"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/";a:1:{s:10:"commentRss";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:53:"https://en.blog.wordpress.com/2016/01/07/canape/feed/";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:38:"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/";a:1:{s:8:"comments";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:1:"1";s:7:"attribs";a:0:{}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}}s:29:"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/";a:2:{s:9:"thumbnail";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:0:"";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:1:{s:3:"url";s:74:"http://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2015/12/canape_responsiveness.png?w=150";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";}}s:7:"content";a:4:{i:0;a:6:{s:4:"data";s:7:"\n			\n		";s:7:"attribs";a:1:{s:0:"";a:2:{s:3:"url";s:74:"http://en-blog.files.wordpress.com/2015/12/canape_responsiveness.png?w=150";s:6:"medium";s:5:"image";}}s:8:"xml_base";s:0:"";s:17:"xml_base_explicit";b:0;s:8:"xml_lang";s:0:"";s:5:"child";a:1:{s:29:"http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/";a:1:{s:5:"title";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:"data";s:23:"Canap